						               													<description>A trivia game with far countries and foreign cultures as a theme. By visiting different continents, you get questions to answer from each country. All correct answers give points in the form of &amp;quot;NF dollars&amp;quot;. Many visits to a country gives you the possibility of gaining a lot of money through the &amp;quot;knowledge ladder&amp;quot; for each country, by answering all of the questions from a card. The money is then multiplied with the number of answered questions for the continent, so some tactics are involved in the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are also certain spaces which gives you possibility to answer questions about images, flags or capitals around the world. These answers give extra money. There is a time limit in the game so you only may answer a certain number of questions (right or wrong) for each continent.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;May also be played with 2-4 teams. The game is based on a Swedish travel reporting program and the title means &amp;quot;Near and Far&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
